  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/PackageDescription\/SupportedPlatform\/WatchOSVersion\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T20:13:44Z\n---\n\n# SupportedPlatform.WatchOSVersion\n\n**Structure**\n\nThe supported watchOS version.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstruct WatchOSVersion\n```\n\n## Type Properties\n\n- **v10**: The value that represents watchOS 10.0.\n- **v11**: The value that represents watchOS 11.0.\n- **v2**: The value that represents watchOS 2.0.\n- **v26**: The value that represents watchOS 26.0.\n- **v3**: The value that represents watchOS 3.0.\n- **v4**: The value that represents watchOS 4.0.\n- **v5**: The value that represents watchOS 5.0.\n- **v6**: The value that represents watchOS 6.0.\n- **v7**: The value that represents watchOS 7.0.\n- **v8**: The value that represents watchOS 8.0.\n- **v9**: The value that represents watchOS 9.0.\n\n## Supporting watchOS\n\n- **watchOS(_:)**: Configure the minimum deployment target version for the watchOS platform.\n- **watchOS(_:)**: Configure the minimum deployment target version for the watchOS platform using a custom version string.\n- **watchOS**: The watchOS platform.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
